TJ

The Person Behind the Booth

Meet Anthony
Gomez

TJ Selfie Station was built on a simple but personal observation. At events, there's always someone who wants to be in the photo but hesitates — backing away from the camera before the moment is captured. As someone who understands that feeling firsthand, Anthony Gomez founded TJ Selfie Station to change that experience entirely.

With a photo booth, the pressure disappears. Silly props, GIFs, instant prints, and short video clips give every guest — regardless of how camera-shy they are — a reason to step in, let loose, and celebrate. That's the experience TJ Selfie Station is built to create at every single event.

What sets us apart isn't just the equipment — it's the genuine care that goes into every booking. When you work with TJ Selfie Station, you're working directly with Anthony, someone who believes that every guest deserves the opportunity to express themselves and walk away with a memory worth keeping.
